                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18151025-13-off71 t18151025-13-crimeloc74"></join>. On the evening of the 23rd of September, a person passing by, told me a boy had stolen a piece of printed cotton from the door. I immediately ran out and caught the prisoner with the printed cotton under his coat; we brought him into the shop and there was a mob wanted to rescue him and get him out. At last 
               <persName id="t18151025-13-person149">
                  John 
                  Ray
               <interp inst="t18151025-13-person149" type="surname" value="Ray"></interp>
