                     <interp inst="t18151025-13-person150" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I was sent for to the prosecutor's house, and when I came there, there was a great mob round the door. Some of them were saying,</p>
               <p>"go it, go it, we will have him out." I went into the shop, and took the prisoner into custody, and going along with him to the watchhouse, I got most violently abused. Here is the cotton.</p>
               <p>Matthew Harrison. That is my master's property.</p>
